  "current_unit": {
    "page_no": 20,
    "unit_id": "p20_g02",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 5,
    "source_text": "儘管2020年的新業務價值27.65億美元較2019年減少了33%，我們迅速採用了新的數碼工具，並且外出限制的普\n遍放寬支持了銷售勢頭的恢復。友邦保險中國業務為2020年本集團的新業務價值帶來最大貢獻，也是我們第一個\n顯示銷售勢頭有所恢復的報告分部，原因在於該地區自2020年3月逐步放寬嚴格的封鎖。撇除維持低位的中國內\n地訪港旅客銷售額，本集團其他分部的新業務價值在下半年強勁復甦，與上半年相比增長了23%。本集團的新業\n務發展勢頭在2021年持續強勁，首兩個月新業務價值較2020年同期高出15%。",
    "current_translation": "Despite VONB of US$2,765 million in 2020 declining by 33% compared to 2019, we rapidly adopted new digital tools, and the widespread relaxation of movement restrictions supported the recovery of sales momentum. AIA China contributed the largest share to the Group's VONB in 2020 and was our first reporting segment to demonstrate recovery in sales momentum, as the region gradually eased strict lockdowns from March 2020 onwards. Excluding the subdued sales from mainland Chinese visitors to Hong Kong, the Group's other segments showed strong recovery in VONB in the second half, growing 23% compared to the first half. The Group's new business development momentum remained robust in 2021, with VONB in the first two months up 15% compared to the same period in 2020."
  },
